title: please explain

embed.description: Stdlol / Platinum 3 0LP / 69W 36L Win Ratio 66% / Zac - 31W 14L Win Ratio 69%, Malzahar - 8W 2L Win Ratio 80%, Kha'Zix - 5W 3L Win Ratio 63%, Lulu - 6W 0L Win Ratio 100%, Nautilus - 4W 0L Win Ratio 100%

body:
how is this guy plat 3 but i know for a fact he has only done 1 placement game this whole season. if you have a look at his amumu ranked game it shows as unranked.

please explain. not hating, 100% curious

cheers

replies.body:
OP.GG doesn't show ranked games past a certain period (I think its 20-30 days). Other than his amumu game (which I assume was for decay), his last ranked play was in the start of April.

He has played all of his placement games and has infact played upwards of 120 soloq games this season. 
The fact his amumu game is showing "level 30" could be due to a recent name change where he took the name from another account.
